(1, 'User Agreement', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#555555\">This document is an electronic record in terms of the Information Technology Act, 2000 and rules made there under as applicable and the amended provisions pertaining to electronic records in various statutes as amended by the Information Technology Act, 2000. This electronic record is generated by a computer system and does not require any physical or digital signatures.</span></span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#555555\">This document is published in accordance with the provisions of Rule 3 (1) of the Information Technology (Intermediaries guidelines) Rules, 2011 that require publishing the rules and regulations, privacy policy and user agreement for access or usage of&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#24a3b5\"><a href=\"http://www.Indocliq.in\" style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#24a3b5\">www.Indocliq</span></a></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#555555\">&nbsp;website.</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#555555\">Your use of the Indocliq website {including </span></span><span style=\"color:blue\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.Indocliq.com\" style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\">www.Indocliq</a></span></u></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#555555\"> an