fy;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#555555\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Any interruption or errors in the operation of the Website.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;montserratregular&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">17. Indemnity</span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#555555\">You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Indocliq and (as applicable) Indocliq&#39;s parent, subsidiaries, affiliates, third-parties and their respective shareholders, officers, directors, agents, and employees, from any losses, liabilities, damages, costs and expenses, claims or demand, or actions including reasonable attorneys&#39; fees asserted against or incurred by Indocliq, made by any third party arising out of Your breach or non-performance of terms of the User Agreement, Indocliq Rules and Policies, or the documents they incorporate by reference, or Your violation of any law, rules or regulations or the rights of a third party.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIndocliq may notify You of any claims which You shall be liable to indemnify Indocliq against. You will then be required to consult with Indocliq regarding the course of action to be undertaken in defending such a claim. Further, You shall not compromise or settle any claim or admit any liability or wrongdoing on the part of Indocliq without the express prior written consent of Indocliq which can be withheld or denied or conditioned by Indocliq in its sole discretion.</span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;montserratregular&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">18. General</span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#5